type="machine">unstable/6026</fr:addr><fr:route>unstable-6026.xml</fr:route><fr:title
text="" /><fr:taxon>Proof</fr:taxon></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter>
 <fr:p>To see that <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[g\colon  B\to  A]]></fr:tex> is unique, we fix any other <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[g']]></fr:tex> that is simultaneously a <fr:link
href="jms-00KS.xml"
title="Section-retraction pair"
addr="jms-00KS"
type="local">retraction</fr:link> and a <fr:link
href="jms-00KS.xml"
title="Section-retraction pair"
addr="jms-00KS"
type="local">section</fr:link> of <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[f]]></fr:tex> and show that <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[g=g']]></fr:tex>:</fr:p>
 <fr:tex
display="block"><![CDATA[
  \begin {aligned}
    g &= \mathsf {id}_{A}\circ  g\\
    &= {\mathopen {}\left (g'\circ  f\right )\mathclose {}} \circ  g\\
    &= g'\circ {\mathopen {}\left (f\circ  g\right )\mathclose {}}\\
    &= g'\circ \mathsf {id}_{B}\\
    &= g'
  \end {aligned}
 ]]></fr:tex>
</fr:mainmatter></fr:tree>
 
